  Bonus Video: Film Posters

In this bonus video, I'll show you how to create film posters utilizing a simple Midjourney, Photoshop, and Gigapixel workflow. It's an incredibly easy and fun way to drum up excitement for your projects.

Remember, you can also use InsightFaceSwap for film posters. This is great if you want to have your film's lead actor be front and center.
